org.fife.ui.rsyntaxtextarea

Class WrappedSyntaxView.WrappedLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.text.View
      • org.fife.ui.rsyntaxtextarea.WrappedSyntaxView.WrappedLine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.SwingConstants
    Enclosing class:
    WrappedSyntaxView

    class WrappedSyntaxView.WrappedLine
extends javax.swing.text.View
    Simple view of a line that wraps if it doesn't fit within the horizontal space allocated. This class tries to be lightweight by carrying little state of it's own and sharing the state of the outer class with it's siblings.
